{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "30ee6f61-1660-4980-9ddd-1f8468ffdf62", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/30ee6f61-1660-4980-9ddd-1f8468ffdf62@1.pkg/1772597490031/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597491156", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/30ee6f61-1660-4980-9ddd-1f8468ffdf62@1.pkg/1772597490031/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597491156"}, "identifier": "30ee6f61-1660-4980-9ddd-1f8468ffdf62", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>本题考查中国发展的机遇。</p>\n\n<p>B:分析题文可知，跨国企业“看好中国”是因为中国拥有雄厚的物质技术基础，这为跨国企业提供了广阔的市场和生产能力。</p>\n\n<p>A、C:中国是世界最二大经济体，也没有全面超越发达国家水平，故说法错误。</p>\n\n<p>C:跨国企业“看好中国”是基于中国的经济发展潜力与合作机遇，而不是中国维护本国核心利益的能力，该选项与题干逻辑不符。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）中国发展高层论坛2025年年会于3月24日在北京落下帷幕。本次论坛吸引了21个国家的86名跨国企业正式代表参加，首次参会的跨国企业数量创新高，体现了跨国企业“看好中国”的信心”。这一信心是基于中国（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编）中国发展高层论坛2025年年会于3月24日在北京落下帷幕。本次论坛吸引了21个国家的86名跨国企业正式代表参加，首次参会的跨国企业数量创新高，体现了跨国企业“看好中国”的信心”。这一信心是基于中国（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/30ee6f61-1660-4980-9ddd-1f8468ffdf62@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755140978462", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "